{
  "texts": [
    "This ensures that their system can generate enhanced prompts for each new query based on user feedback.",
    "In contrast, Lazaridou et al. (2022) uses few-shot prompts and answer reordering to improve inference computation.",
    "As defined in Section 2 on Parallel Interaction, this interaction is inspired by the K-Nearest Neighbor (KNN) LM (Khandelwal et al., 2019).",
    "It is a paradigmatic instance of RALM, wherein the LM is employed solely to enhance the outcomes.",
    "Since the proposal of KNN-LM, many researchers have worked to optimize the model."
  ]
}